## 7. Caching (`ai_shared.cache`)

```python
from ai_shared.cache import ExactCache, SemanticCache, RedisCache, MultiLayerCache

# ── Exact Cache — deterministic hash-based ──
exact = ExactCache(ttl_seconds=1800)

# ── Semantic Cache — near-duplicate detection via embeddings ──
semantic = SemanticCache(
    embedding_model="text-embedding-3-small",
    similarity_threshold=0.97,
    ttl_seconds=3600,
)

# ── Redis-backed Cache ──
redis_cache = RedisCache(
    url="redis://localhost:6379",
    ttl_seconds=3600,
    key_prefix="ai:",
)

# ── Multi-Layer Cache (L1 memory → L2 Redis) ──
cache = MultiLayerCache(
    layers=[exact, redis_cache],      # checked in order
)

# ── Unified usage pattern ──
result = await cache.get(query)
if result is None:
    result = await rag.query(query)
    await cache.set(query, result)

# ── Statistics ──
stats = cache.stats()
# {"hits": 1423, "misses": 87, "hit_rate": 0.942, "size_bytes": 20480}
```

