## 8. Security Utilities (`ai_shared.security`)

```python
from ai_shared.security import PIIDetector, ContentFilter, InputValidator, PIIType

# ── PII Detection & Redaction ──
detector = PIIDetector(
    engine="presidio",                  # presidio | regex | llm
    entities=[
        PIIType.PERSON,
        PIIType.EMAIL,
        PIIType.PHONE,
        PIIType.SSN,
        PIIType.CREDIT_CARD,
    ],
)

result = detector.detect("John Doe's email is john@example.com")
redacted = detector.redact("John Doe's email is john@example.com")
# "[PERSON]'s email is [EMAIL]"

# ── Content Filtering ──
content_filter = ContentFilter(
    block_categories=["violence", "hate_speech", "sexual_content"],
    check_input=True,
    check_output=True,
)

is_safe = await content_filter.check(user_input)

# ── Input Validation ──
validator = InputValidator(
    max_length=10000,
    allowed_languages=["en", "es", "fr"],
    block_injection_patterns=True,
)

validated = validator.validate(user_input)
```

