## 11. Plugin System (`ai_shared.plugins`)

```python
from ai_shared.plugins import PluginRegistry, PluginMetadata

# ── Create a registry ──
registry = PluginRegistry()

# ── Register a custom vector store plugin ──
registry.register(
    MyCustomVectorStore,
    metadata=PluginMetadata(
        name="my_vectorstore",
        version="1.0.0",
        description="Custom vector store adapter",
        category="vectorstore",
    ),
)

# ── Load and initialize a plugin ──
plugin_instance = registry.load("my_vectorstore", config={"host": "localhost"})
plugin_instance.initialize(config={"collection": "docs"})

# ── Register a hook for pipeline events ──
registry.register_hook("pre_ingest", my_validation_hook)
registry.register_hook("post_query", my_audit_hook)

# ── Fire hooks ──
await registry.fire_hook("pre_ingest", documents=docs)

# ── List available plugins ──
for entry in registry.list_plugins():
    print(f"{entry.metadata.name} v{entry.metadata.version} [{entry.metadata.category}]")
```

### Plugin Categories

| Category | Use Case |
|---|---|
| `vectorstore` | Custom vector database adapters |
| `embedding` | Custom embedding providers |
| `chunking` | Domain-specific chunking strategies |
| `llm` | Custom LLM provider integrations |
| `search` | Custom retrieval strategies |
| `reranker` | Custom reranking models |

